  <entry>
    <title>树莓派连接摄像头</title>
    <link href="https://ccw1996.github.io/2020/10/18/%E6%A0%91%E8%8E%93%E6%B4%BE%E8%BF%9E%E6%8E%A5%E6%91%84%E5%83%8F%E5%A4%B4/"/>
    <id>https://ccw1996.github.io/2020/10/18/%E6%A0%91%E8%8E%93%E6%B4%BE%E8%BF%9E%E6%8E%A5%E6%91%84%E5%83%8F%E5%A4%B4/</id>
    <published>2020-10-18T08:20:33.000Z</published>
    <updated>2020-10-18T08:35:30.000Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<blockquote><p>注：在写该博文时，使用 树莓派 4B 8GB 版本，Ubuntu MATE 20.04.1 Beta 2 - 13 August 2020。摄像头型号为官方的 Pi Camera V2</p></blockquote><p>树莓派在使用官方的 Raspberry Pi OS 时，可以使用 <code>raspi-config</code> 直接使能摄像头，然后即可使用。但在 Ubuntu Mate 20 中，因为种种原因，并不包含 <code>raspi-config</code> 。同时，通过修改 apt 源之后，再启用 <code>raspi-config</code> 时，会提示 </p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tbody><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">Your firmware appears to be out of date(no start_x.elf). Please update.</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure><p></p><p>但是，的确是存在 <code>start_x.elf</code> 文件。</p><p>可以通过以下方法去使能官方摄像头，也就是通过 CSI 方式启用的摄像头：</p><ol type="1"><li><code>cd /boot/firmware</code></li><li><code>vim config.txt</code></li><li>在最底下的位置添加一行 <code>start_x=1</code></li><li>重启 raspberry-pi</li></ol><p>重启之后，在命令行输入 <code>raspivid -p 0,0,640,480 -t 0</code> 应该就能够看到摄像头的实时画面了。</p>]]></content>
    
    
      
      
    <summary type="html">&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;注：在写该博文时，使用 树莓派 4B 8GB 版本，Ubuntu MATE 20.04.1 Beta 2 - 13 August 2020。摄像头型号为官方的 Pi Camera V2&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;树莓派在使用官方的 </summary>
      
    
    
    
    
    <category term="raspberry_pi" scheme="https://ccw1996.github.io/tags/raspberry-pi/"/>
    
  </entry>
  
  <entry>
    <title>C++ 中的智能指针</title>
    <link href="https://ccw1996.github.io/2020/08/30/auto-ptr/"/>
    <id>https://ccw1996.github.io/2020/08/30/auto-ptr/</id>
    <published>2020-08-30T03:21:53.000Z</published>
    <updated>2020-10-05T05:14:19.000Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="c中的智能指针">C++ 中的智能指针</h1><p>C++ 有四种智能指针，其中 auto_ptr 已经被 C++ 11 抛弃，在工程中主要使用 <code>unique_ptr</code> <code>shared_ptr</code> 和 <code>weak_ptr</code></p><h2 id="unique_ptr">unique_ptr</h2><p>unique_ptr 实现的是全局唯一指针，保证同一时间内只有一个智能指针可以指向该对象。</p><figure class="highlight cpp"><table><tbody><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="built_in">unique_ptr</span>&lt;<span class="keyword">int</span>&gt; <span class="title">p3</span><span class="params">(<span class="keyword">new</span> <span class="keyword">int</span>())</span></span>;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">unique_ptr</span>&lt;<span class="keyword">int</span>&gt; p4;</span><br><span class="line">p4=p3; <span class="comment">//error</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure><p>unique_ptr 不允许拷贝和赋值。如果说希望把之前的指针转移到另一个变量上，则可以使用 <code>std::move()</code> 函数转移指针所有权。</p><figure class="highlight cpp"><table><tbody><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="built_in">unique_ptr</span>&lt;<span class="built_in">string</span>&gt; ps1, ps2;</span><br><span class="line">ps1 = demo(<span class="string">"hello"</span>);</span><br><span class="line">ps2 = move(ps1);</span><br><span class="line">ps1 = demo(<span class="string">"alexia"</span>);</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">cout</span> &lt;&lt; *ps2 &lt;&lt; *ps1 &lt;&lt; <span class="built_in">endl</span>;</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure><p>当然，不可拷贝和赋值这一操作也有例外，我们可以拷贝或赋值一个将要被销毁的 unique_ptr。</p><figure class="highlight cpp"><table><tbody><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">//从函数返回一个unique_ptr</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="built_in">unique_ptr</span> <span class="title">func1</span><span class="params">(<span class="keyword">int</span> a)</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"></span>{</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="built_in">unique_ptr</span>&lt;<span class="keyword">int</span>&gt; (<span class="keyword">new</span> <span class="keyword">int</span>(a));</span><br><span class="line">}</span><br><span class="line"> </span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">//返回一个局部对象的拷贝</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="built_in">unique_ptr</span> <span class="title">func2</span><span class="params">(<span class="keyword">int</span> a)</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"></span>{</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="function"><span class="built_in">unique_ptr</span>&lt;<span class="keyword">int</span>&gt; <span class="title">up</span><span class="params">(<span class="keyword">new</span> <span class="keyword">int</span>(a))</span></span>;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> up;</span><br><span class="line">}</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure><h2 id="shared_ptr">shared_ptr</h2><p>shared_ptr 实现共享式拥有概念，使用计数机制来表明资源被指针共享。</p><p>成员函数：</p><p>use_count 返回引用计数的个数</p><p>unique 返回是否是独占所有权 (use_count 为 1)</p><p>swap 交换两个 shared_ptr 对象 (即交换所拥有的对象)</p><p>reset 放弃内部对象的所有权或拥有对象的变更，会引起原有对象的引用计数的减少</p><p>get 返回内部对象 (指针)</p><h2 id="weak_ptr">weak_ptr</h2><p>share_ptr 虽然已经很好用了，但是有一点 share_ptr 智能指针还是有内存泄露的情况，当两个对象相互使用一个 shared_ptr 成员变量指向对方，会造成循环引用，使引用计数失效，从而导致内存泄漏。</p><p>weak_ptr 是一种不控制对象生命周期的智能指针，它指向一个 shared_ptr 管理的对象。进行该对象的内存管理的是那个强引用的 shared_ptr， weak_ptr 只是提供了对管理对象的一个访问手段。weak_ptr 设计的目的是为配合 shared_ptr 而引入的一种智能指针来协助 shared_ptr 工作，它只可以从一个 shared_ptr 或另一个 weak_ptr 对象构造，它的构造和析构不会引起引用记数的增加或减少。</p><h2 id="new-和-make_shared-在内存上的区别">new 和 make_shared 在内存上的区别</h2><p>先 new 然后赋值的方式，会导致内存碎片化</p><p>make_shared 的方法分配内存，不会导致内存产生过多的碎片</p>]]></content>
    
    
      
      
    <summary type="html">&lt;h1 id=&quot;c中的智能指针&quot;&gt;C++ 中的智能指针&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;C++ 有四种智能指针，其中 auto_ptr 已经被 C++ 11 抛弃，在工程中主要使用 &lt;code&gt;unique_ptr&lt;/code&gt; &lt;code&gt;shared_ptr&lt;/code&gt; 和 &lt;code&gt;w</summary>
      
    
    
    
    
    <category term="cpp" scheme="https://ccw1996.github.io/tags/cpp/"/>
    
  </entry>
  
  <entry>
    <title>使用 tensorflow2 训练 Titanic 数据集</title>
    <link href="https://ccw1996.github.io/2020/06/06/titanic/"/>
    <id>https://ccw1996.github.io/2020/06/06/titanic/</id>
    <published>2020-06-06T09:21:35.000Z</published>
    <updated>2020-06-07T04:31:46.000Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="对数据进行预处理">对数据进行预处理</h2><p>数据分为两个 csv，一个是训练用数据集 (train.csv), 一个是测试用数据集 (test.csv)。先读取这些数据。</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tbody><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment">#载入数据</span></span><br><span class="line">train = pd.read_csv(<span class="string">'train.csv'</span>)</span><br><span class="line">test = pd.read_csv(<span class="string">'test.csv'</span>)</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">#合并前在每个数据集中添加一列</span></span><br><span class="line">train[<span class="string">'Type'</span>] = <span class="string">'train'</span></span><br><span class="line">test[<span class="string">'Type'</span>] = <span class="string">'test'</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">#合并训练和测试数据</span></span><br><span class="line">data = train.append(test, sort=<span class="literal">False</span>)</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure><h3 id="特征工程">特征工程</h3><figure class="highlight python"><table><tbody><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment">#提取每列名称</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">for</span> name_string <span class="keyword">in</span> data[<span class="string">'Name'</span>]:</span><br><span class="line">    data[<span class="string">'Title'</span>] = data[<span class="string">'Name'</span>].<span class="built_in">str</span>.extract(<span class="string">'([A-Za-z]+)\.'</span>, expand=<span class="literal">True</span>)</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">#删除没有价值的列</span></span><br><span class="line">mapping = {<span class="string">'Mlle'</span>: <span class="string">'Miss'</span>, <span class="string">'Ms'</span>: <span class="string">'Miss'</span>, <span class="string">'Mme'</span>: <span class="string">'Mrs'</span>, <span class="string">'Major'</span>: <span class="string">'Other'</span>, </span><br><span class="line">           <span class="string">'Col'</span>: <span class="string">'Other'</span>, <span class="string">'Dr'</span> : <span class="string">'Other'</span>, <span class="string">'Rev'</span> : <span class="string">'Other'</span>, <span class="string">'Capt'</span>: <span class="string">'Other'</span>, </span><br><span class="line">           <span class="string">'Jonkheer'</span>: <span class="string">'Royal'</span>, <span class="string">'Sir'</span>: <span class="string">'Royal'</span>, <span class="string">'Lady'</span>: <span class="string">'Royal'</span>, </span><br><span class="line">           <span class="string">'Don'</span>: <span class="string">'Royal'</span>, <span class="string">'Countess'</span>: <span class="string">'Royal'</span>, <span class="string">'Dona'</span>: <span class="string">'Royal'</span>}      </span><br><span class="line">data.replace({<span class="string">'Title'</span>: mapping}, inplace=<span class="literal">True</span>)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">#将Parch和SibSp合并到一个名为Family_Size的列中。</span></span><br><span class="line">data[<span class="string">'Family_Size'</span>] = (data[<span class="string">'Parch'</span>] + data[<span class="string">'SibSp'</span>]).astype(<span class="built_in">int</span>)</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure><h3 id="填充缺失的数据">填充缺失的数据</h3><p>有两种方法解决数据集有缺失的情况： 1. 删除此行 2. 用均值、中位数填充 </p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tbody><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment">#用均值填充年龄</span></span><br><span class="line">data[<span class="string">'Age'</span>].fillna(data.groupby([<span class="string">"Sex"</span>, <span class="string">"Pclass"</span>])[<span class="string">'Age'</span>].transform(<span class="string">"mean"</span>), inplace=<span class="literal">True</span>)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">#手动添加Embarked</span></span><br><span class="line">data.loc[<span class="number">61</span>,<span class="string">'Embarked'</span>] = <span class="string">'S'</span></span><br><span class="line">data.loc[<span class="number">829</span>,<span class="string">'Embarked'</span>] = <span class="string">'S'</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 票价用均值填充</span></span><br><span class="line">data[<span class="string">'Fare'</span>].fillna(data[<span class="string">'Fare'</span>].mean(), inplace = <span class="literal">True</span>)</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure><p></p><h3 id="用连续的值编码类别">用连续的值编码类别</h3><figure class="highlight python"><table><tbody><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment">#删除模型中不会使用的变量</span></span><br><span class="line">data.drop([<span class="string">'Cabin'</span>, <span class="string">'Name'</span>, <span class="string">'Ticket'</span>, <span class="string">'PassengerId'</span>, <span class="string">'SibSp'</span>, <span class="string">'Parch'</span>], axis=<span class="number">1</span>, inplace=<span class="literal">True</span>)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 转换类别的类型</span></span><br><span class="line">data[<span class="string">'Sex'</span>] = data[<span class="string">'Sex'</span>].astype(<span class="string">'category'</span>)</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 转换类别的编码</span></span><br><span class="line">data[<span class="string">'Sex'</span>] = data[<span class="string">'Sex'</span>].cat.codes</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 对类编进行编码</span></span><br><span class="line">categorical = [<span class="string">'Embarked'</span>, <span class="string">'Title'</span>, <span class="string">'Pclass'</span>]</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">for</span> cat <span class="keyword">in</span> categorical:</span><br><span class="line">    data = pd.concat([data, </span><br><span class="line">                    pd.get_dummies(data[cat], prefix=cat)], axis=<span class="number">1</span>)</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">del</span> data[cat]</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 缩放值到0-1之间</span></span><br><span class="line">continuous = [<span class="string">'Age'</span>, <span class="string">'Fare'</span>, <span class="string">'Family_Size'</span>]</span><br><span class="line">scaler = StandardScaler()</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">for</span> val <span class="keyword">in</span> continuous:</span><br><span class="line">    data[val] = data[val].astype(<span class="string">'float64'</span>)</span><br><span class="line">    data[val] = scaler.fit_transform(data[val].values.reshape(-<span class="number">1</span>, <span class="number">1</span>))</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 分离训练和测试集</span></span><br><span class="line">train = data[data[<span class="string">'Type'</span>] == <span class="string">'train'</span>].drop(columns = [<span class="string">'Type'</span>, <span class="string">'Survived'</span>])</span><br><span class="line">train_ = data[data[<span class="string">'Type'</span>] == <span class="string">'train'</span>][<span class="string">'Survived'</span>]</span><br><span class="line">X_train = train.values</span><br><span class="line">y_train = train_.values</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">test = data[data[<span class="string">'Type'</span>] == <span class="string">'test'</span>].drop(columns = [<span class="string">'Type'</span>, <span class="string">'Survived'</span>])</span><br><span class="line">X_test = test.values</span><br><span class="line">X_test = X_test.astype(np.float64, copy=<span class="literal">False</span>)</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure><h2 id="使用tensorflow构建模型">使用 tensorflow 构建模型</h2><h3 id="模型构建">模型构建</h3><figure class="highlight python"><table><tbody><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 构建一个简单的模型</span></span><br><span class="line">model1 = keras.models.Sequential()</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">model1.add(keras.layers.Dense(<span class="number">18</span>, input_dim = X_train.shape[<span class="number">1</span>], activation = keras.activations.relu))</span><br><span class="line">model1.add(keras.layers.Dense(<span class="number">8</span>, activation = keras.activations.relu))</span><br><span class="line">model1.add(keras.layers.Dense(<span class="number">1</span>, activation = keras.activations.sigmoid))</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 可视化模型</span></span><br><span class="line">model1.summary()</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure><h3 id="编译模型">编译模型</h3><p>模型编译有三个参数： 1. optimizer 可以选择 adam 或者 sgd 2. loss 常见的是 mse 或者 categorical_crossentropy 或者是 binary_crossentropy。损失函数可以通过名称指定，也可以通过 tf.keras.losses 模块传递可调用对象来指定。 3. metrics 用于监视培训。这些是来自 tf.keras.metrics 模块的字符串名称或可调用项。 </p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tbody><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">model1.<span class="built_in">compile</span>(optimizer = keras.optimizers.SGD(), </span><br><span class="line">               loss = keras.losses.binary_crossentropy, </span><br><span class="line">               metrics = [tf.keras.metrics.binary_accuracy])</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure><p></p><h3 id="训练模型">训练模型</h3><p>tf.keras.Model.fit 接受三个重要参数： 1. epochs 2. batch_size 3. validation_data 4. validation_split 与 validation_data 相同，但是使用训练数据的一小部分作为验证数据。模型将分开训练数据的这一部分，不对其进行训练，并且将在每个时期结束时评估此数据的损失和任何模型度量。 </p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tbody><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">history = model1.fit(X_train, y_train, epochs=<span class="number">100</span>, validation_split=<span class="number">0.2</span>)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">val_acc = np.mean(history.history[<span class="string">'val_binary_accuracy'</span>])</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure><p></p><h3 id="预测测试数据并提交给kaggle">预测测试数据并提交给 Kaggle</h3><figure class="highlight python"><table><tbody><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">submission = pd.read_csv(<span class="string">"gender_submission.csv"</span>, index_col=<span class="string">'PassengerId'</span>)</span><br><span class="line">submission[<span class="string">'Survived'</span>] = model1.predict(X_test)</span><br><span class="line">submission[<span class="string">'Survived'</span>] = submission[<span class="string">'Survived'</span>].apply(<span class="keyword">lambda</span> x: <span class="built_in">round</span>(x,<span class="number">0</span>)).astype(<span class="string">'int'</span>)</span><br><span class="line">submission.to_csv(<span class="string">'Titanic_model1.csv'</span>)</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure><h2 id="使用-function-api创建模型">使用 Function API 创建模型</h2><figure class="highlight python"><table><tbody><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 创建模型</span></span><br><span class="line">input_ = keras.layers.Input(shape=X_train.shape[<span class="number">1</span>:])</span><br><span class="line">hidden1 = keras.layers.Dense(<span class="number">36</span>, activation=<span class="string">"elu"</span>)(input_)</span><br><span class="line">drop1 = keras.layers.Dropout(rate=<span class="number">0.2</span>)(hidden1)</span><br><span class="line">hidden2 = keras.layers.Dense(<span class="number">18</span>, activation=<span class="string">"elu"</span>)(drop1)</span><br><span class="line">drop2 = keras.layers.Dropout(rate=<span class="number">0.2</span>)(hidden2)</span><br><span class="line">hidden3 = keras.layers.Dense(<span class="number">8</span>, activation=<span class="string">"elu"</span>)(drop2)</span><br><span class="line">output = keras.layers.Dense(<span class="number">1</span>, activation=<span class="string">"sigmoid"</span>)(hidden3)</span><br><span class="line">model2 = keras.models.Model(inputs=[input_], outputs=[output])</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 打印模型</span></span><br><span class="line">model2.summary()</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 编译模型</span></span><br><span class="line">model2.<span class="built_in">compile</span>(optimizer = <span class="string">'nadam'</span>, </span><br><span class="line">               loss = <span class="string">'binary_crossentropy'</span>, </span><br><span class="line">               metrics = [<span class="string">'accuracy'</span>])</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 配置提前停止并恢复最佳权重</span></span><br><span class="line">early_stopping_cb = keras.callbacks.EarlyStopping(patience=<span class="number">10</span>, restore_best_weights=<span class="literal">True</span>)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">history2 = model2.fit(X_train, y_train, epochs=<span class="number">100</span>, validation_split=<span class="number">0.2</span>, callbacks=[early_stopping_cb])</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">val_acc = np.mean(history2.history[<span class="string">'val_accuracy'</span>])</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 进行预测</span></span><br><span class="line">submission2 = pd.read_csv(<span class="string">"gender_submission.csv"</span>, index_col=<span class="string">'PassengerId'</span>)</span><br><span class="line">submission2[<span class="string">'Survived'</span>] = model2.predict(X_test)</span><br><span class="line">submission2[<span class="string">'Survived'</span>] = submission[<span class="string">'Survived'</span>].apply(<span class="keyword">lambda</span> x: <span class="built_in">round</span>(x,<span class="number">0</span>)).astype(<span class="string">'int'</span>)</span><br><span class="line">submission2.to_csv(<span class="string">'Titanic_model2.csv'</span>)</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure><h2 id="超参数调整">超参数调整</h2><figure class="highlight python"><table><tbody><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">def</span> <span class="title">build_model</span>(<span class="params">input_shape=[<span class="number">16</span>], n_hidden=<span class="number">1</span>, n_neurons=<span class="number">30</span>, activation = <span class="string">'relu'</span>, optimizer = <span class="string">'SGD'</span></span>):</span></span><br><span class="line">    model = keras.models.Sequential()</span><br><span class="line">    model.add(keras.layers.InputLayer(input_shape=input_shape))</span><br><span class="line">    i = <span class="number">1</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">for</span> layer <span class="keyword">in</span> <span class="built_in">range</span>(n_hidden):</span><br><span class="line">        model.add(keras.layers.Dense(n_neurons/i, activation=activation))</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">if</span> n_neurons &gt; <span class="number">20</span>:</span><br><span class="line">            model.add(keras.layers.Dropout(rate=<span class="number">0.2</span>))</span><br><span class="line">            i = i + <span class="number">2</span></span><br><span class="line">    model.add(keras.layers.Dense(<span class="number">1</span>, activation=<span class="string">'sigmoid'</span>))</span><br><span class="line">    model.<span class="built_in">compile</span>(loss=<span class="string">"binary_crossentropy"</span>, optimizer=optimizer, metrics=[<span class="string">'accuracy'</span>])</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> model</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure><p>与此同时，使用以下两个 API 对模型进行封装 - KerasClassifier：Keras 的 scikit-learn 分类器 API 的实现。 - KerasRegressor：用于 Keras 的 scikit-learn 回归 API 的实现。</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tbody><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">model3 = keras.wrappers.scikit_learn.KerasClassifier(build_fn=build_model)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">history3 = model3.fit(X_train, y_train, epochs=<span class="number">100</span>,</span><br><span class="line">              validation_split=<span class="number">0.2</span>,</span><br><span class="line">              callbacks=[keras.callbacks.EarlyStopping(patience=<span class="number">10</span>)])</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">val_acc = np.mean(history3.history[<span class="string">'val_accuracy'</span>])</span><br><span class="line">print(<span class="string">"\n%s: %.2f%%"</span> % (<span class="string">'val_acc'</span>, val_acc*<span class="number">100</span>))</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure><p>如果要随机搜索超参数，则如下： </p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tbody><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">from</span> sklearn.model_selection <span class="keyword">import</span> RandomizedSearchCV</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">param_distribs = {</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="string">"n_hidden"</span>: [<span class="number">1</span>, <span class="number">2</span>, <span class="number">3</span>, <span class="number">4</span>],</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="string">"n_neurons"</span>: [<span class="number">6</span>, <span class="number">18</span>, <span class="number">30</span>, <span class="number">42</span>, <span class="number">56</span>, <span class="number">77</span>, <span class="number">84</span>, <span class="number">100</span>],</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="string">"activation"</span>: [<span class="string">'relu'</span>, <span class="string">'selu'</span>, <span class="string">'elu'</span>],</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="string">"optimizer"</span>: [<span class="string">'SGD'</span>, <span class="string">'RMSprop'</span>, <span class="string">'Adam'</span>],</span><br><span class="line">}</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">rnd_search_cv = RandomizedSearchCV(model3, param_distribs, n_iter=<span class="number">10</span>, cv=<span class="number">3</span>, verbose=<span class="number">2</span>)</span><br><span class="line">rnd_search_cv.fit(X_train, y_train, epochs=<span class="number">100</span>, validation_split=<span class="number">0.2</span>)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 打印最佳的查参数</span></span><br><span class="line">rnd_search_cv.best_params_</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure><p></p><p>如果找到了更好的超参数，则可以轻松使用 </p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tbody><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">model4 = build_model(n_hidden=<span class="number">4</span>, n_neurons=<span class="number">77</span>, input_shape=[<span class="number">16</span>], activation = <span class="string">'elu'</span>, optimizer = <span class="string">'Adam'</span>)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">print(model4.summary())</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">history4 = model4.fit(X_train, y_train, epochs=<span class="number">100</span>,</span><br><span class="line">                     validation_split=<span class="number">0.2</span>, callbacks=[early_stopping_cb])</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure><p></p><blockquote><p>参考链接</p><p>https://dev-state.com/posts/tf_keras_1/</p></blockquote>]]></content>
    
    
      
      
